6) IMPLEMENTATION OF FULL OUTER JOIN OPERATION 
11  
SQL> SELECT e.emp_id, e.emp_name, e.joining_date, d.department, d.location 
2 FROM employee_info e 
3 FULL OUTER JOIN department_info d 
4 ON e.emp_id = d.emp_id; 
 
